text: Sandra del Castillo (born 26 August 1959) is a Mexican equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
